Package org.eclipse.collections.impl.factory Description

This package contains static utilities for creating mutable and immutable collection factories.
See Also:
for creating Lists, for creating Sets, for creating SortedSets, for creating Bags, for creating Stacks, for creating Maps, for creating SortedMaps, for creating BiMaps, for creating Multimaps, for creating Sets with HashingStrategy, for creating Maps with HashingStrategy, for static import friendly shortcuts for creating Lists, Sets, Bags and Maps
